overview: One of SeanCody's best and brightest models, not to mention one of our most popular, is the epitome of versatility. He can give it as well as he can take it, and he loves it either way. We don't know where he finds the energy and stamina to keep going as long and as hard as he does, but we bow down to his sexual powers. He is definitely a to be reckoned with. It would appear that Tanner doesn't really have a preference when it comes to guys, because whether he's paired with a tall muscle man or a smaller framed boy next door, his chemistry is electric. All of our models love working with him, he's just an easy going guy. He makes you feel like you've known him your whole life. In Tanner 2, you'll see 3 of Tanner's most famous scenes as a top and one of our favorites of him bottoming. Sit back and get to know Tanner, all over again!
title: Tanner 2
